      • addGeofence

        private void addGeofence(DetectedLocation detectedLocation,
                         long RADIUS,
                         int LOITERING_DELAY,
                         String caller)
        Adds a geofence for the transition type GEOFENCE_TRANSITION_DWELL or GEOFENCE_TRANSITION_EXIT
        Parameters:
        detectedLocation - DetectedLocation object containing the coordinates of the geofence
        RADIUS - radius of the geofence
        LOITERING_DELAY - time in milliseconds the user has to dwell in the geofence for triggering the transition type GEOFENCE_TRANSITION_DWELL
        caller - for logging debug information
        See Also:
        DetectedLocation
